Package: ctasapp
Title: Shiny App to Visualize ctas Output
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R:
    person("Björn", "Koneswarakantha", , "bjoern.koneswarakantha@roche.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Interactive Shiny application for exploring results from the
    ctas (Clinical Timeseries Anomaly Spotter) R package. Provides
    drill-down visualizations of site-level outlier scores and
    subject-level time series data.
